# AutoMFlows (Cursor)

**Operating contract:** read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) first (install, verify commands, secrets, PR checklist).

## Monorepo (npm workspaces)

Root [package.json](../../package.json) workspaces: `backend`, `frontend`, `shared`, `mcp-server`. Prefer root scripts: `npm run lint`, `npm run type-check`, `npm test`, `npm run build`, `npm start`.

Build `@automflows/shared` before backend/frontend type-check or build that depends on it: `npm run build --workspace=shared`.

## Playwright / postinstall

[backend/package.json](../../backend/package.json) defines `postinstall`: `npx playwright install chromium`. It runs when backend dependencies install (e.g. root `npm ci`). The backend execution engine uses Playwright; integration tests may assume Chromium is available.

## Workflow JSON and test resources

- **Workflow fixtures:** primarily under `tests/workflows/` (e.g. `tests/workflows/demo/*.json`).
- **Supporting data:** `tests/resources/` (JSON, CSV, env samples, etc.).

Do not commit real secrets; use [`.env.example`](../../.env.example) for variable names only.

